Ranger Help for: rdefend
========================

SYNTAX:      rdefend
USAGE:       Any terrain

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to adopt a defensive combat stance. While
in defensive stance, the Ranger prioritizes evasion and blocking over
attacking, gaining improved damage reduction and dodge chance at the
cost of reduced offensive output. This stance is useful when facing
overwhelming odds or when the Ranger needs to survive long enough for
help to arrive. Use 'rdefend' again to return to normal stance.
